48
00:02:42.620 --> 00:02:46.329
binds DNA, deregulates retinoic acid signaling, and is

49
00:02:46.380 --> 00:02:49.600
clearly the basis for the exquisite retinoic acid

50
00:02:49.640 --> 00:02:51.740
